{
  "stem": "2522.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then one day, I think it was early in '39-- and there was quite a bit of money there, I understand.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My father said, well, I, I really need the money because I-- my-- Mr.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Kubicek was going to go to the Zionist Congress in either Basel-- I think it was in Basel in 1939.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He was the delegate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the idea was that he was going to go out, take the money out, get the visa, and we will all go out.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "My mother goes upstairs, opens the cigarette box, which was a metal box, and all the money was charred, fell apart.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] She put the cigar box behind a radiator, you know, sort of tucked it away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Apparently, when she put it in, it didn't fall down, it stayed up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it was the heat from the steam radiator.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The only thing that I remember, and I tell it to my children, is my father didn't say a word of reproach to my mother.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But Kubicek went out to Basel-- yeah, it was Basel; it was the Zionist Congress in Basel-- and started making arrangements.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Of course, we really didn't have money by that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Also, my father was very much torn because his parents were still living.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they would not move.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They just absolutely refused.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then he had sisters and all kinds of obligations.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was one of these things where, well, let's postpone it for another month.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I mean, it was never this absolute feeling of urgency.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "OK, now we cut it and go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] It was this continual negotiation, which is a theme that very much emerges in my life in my observation of the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
